{"tid":1405954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【8.5大罷工】民航處三分一交通管制員集體請病假 即日按章工作促回應五大訴求","createTime":"2019-08-04T11:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T04:20:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3a678b56ede48a2db70f2a822d3285d6371d8c36","tid":1405954,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:43:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190804/59896545\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190804%2F59896545&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB1e0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=ed7c4280\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190804%2F59896545&h=e1a6475f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190804/59896545</a><br />\n<br />\n【8.5大罷工】民航處三分一交通管制員集體請病假 即日按章工作促回應五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190804/large/1564915216_950f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190804%2Flarge%2F1564915216_950f.png&h=dc4c3acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n (資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n全港發動8月5日「三罷」，《蘋果》獲悉，民航處約三分之一的航空交通管制員今日集體請病假。據了解，現時民航處每日約有90名航空交通管制員負責處理機場航班升降及運作，但約三分之一的航空交通管制員今日請病假。而民航處已即時聯絡候命員工頂替病假的員工上班。《蘋果》已向民航處查詢，正等候回覆。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【逆權運動】撐公務員後遭政府「翻舊賬」 王永平反駁冇矛盾：政治中立是整體看法<br />\n<br />\n此外，有航空交通管制員以「機場前線公務員，帶領香港人守護年輕一代」為題發表聲明，斥特區政府刻意縱容前線警員濫用暴力、漠視「無證綠衫軍」在街上執行所謂的「警權」；在民居旁、鬧市中舉起雷明登霰彈槍，把香港長久以來的法治制度送上絕路，明言最近香港的天空「變了色」。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指去年「山竹」襲港，而今年突如其來的「韋帕」，前線人手雖然極為緊絀，「但我們堅守崗位，並維持香港機場24小時的安全運作。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【逆權運動】老伯遭防暴警近距離噴椒後跌倒 英勇市民上前抬走救治<br />\n<br />\n聲明強烈譴責有民航處的員工及管理層刻意製造白色恐怖，即日起將按章工作，待時機成熟，更不排除罷工的可能性，直至政府正面回應民間五大訴求。他們希望藉此呼籲各界，特別是航空界同業，參與8月5日的「全港三罷，七區集會」，向年青人表明，「你們並不孤單。作為航空交通管制員，我們的專業與良知，與你們同行，守護我們的未來。」<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【每周送10萬】<br />\n升級壹會員獨家尊享，立即參加10萬火急大抽獎 !<br />\n*推廣生意的競賽牌照號碼：52302-9  <br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【8.5大罷工】市民自製車窗貼紙籲「安全駕駛」 社工設「樹窿」助人抒發情緒<br />\n<br />\n【逆權運動】撐公務員後遭政府「翻舊賬」 王永平反駁冇矛盾：政治中立是整體看法<br />\n【逆權運動】老伯遭防暴警近距離噴椒後跌倒 英勇市民上前抬走救治<br />\n【逆權小店】荃灣雪糕店變身物資站 貫徹兄弟爬山口號 各大食店老闆響應罷工：各自崗位做不同的事<br />\n【逆權運動】絕食陳伯黃大仙被打 強烈譴責警方暴行<br />\n【逆權運動】將軍澳警署落閘 示威者擲蛋後再出巨型丫叉射磚頭毀窗<br />\n【逆權運動】警方：衝突中至少拘捕20人 拒正面回應記者被噴胡椒<br />\n【逆權運動】警察家屬棍毆街坊 掟水彈玻璃樽 警支援家屬向街坊掟催淚彈<br />\n【逆權運動】防暴警驅散黃大仙街坊 龍翔道重開"},{"pid":"dcd34dc9ca2aee9fc0cef58787cb0ba82628bb49","tid":1405954,"uid":265877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:00:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a3ffcee1c52e97d03e08d7dde8608936bbe68021","tid":1405954,"uid":265877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:01:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tHwfo3A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtHwfo3A.jpg&h=7b279fd9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e27abf9d2b4000ad49075d706bf09a46de4a9c8a","tid":1405954,"uid":270377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b036aa5d54f525b1dcfe05103c5108d8c795f2","tid":1405954,"uid":270377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:02:37.000Z","msg":"推完先睇"},{"pid":"ab7e9972b3608c301d09e86d556e628a07922dc0","tid":1405954,"uid":40286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:02:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係時候轉下玩法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同狗打 對政府冇影響 <br />\n對真係揸權嘅土共更加冇影響<br />\n要一針見血 就要搵政權最著緊嘅野同佢玩 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">錢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[不合作運動全面升級] 不論和理非/勇武，入一入嚟。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1403657</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f140e3396fd2083058d9bab47e7fd2eb6009aeae","tid":1405954,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:03:03.000Z","msg":"respect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef871311ed091ad84de34f3ffaeb8f9853e204b3","tid":1405954,"uid":78873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:03:11.000Z","msg":"嘩　呢次真係爆了"},{"pid":"87cc62c7920218e5f5bc3bd33f5432da6605d186","tid":1405954,"uid":227748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:11:48.000Z","msg":"好堅，聽講勁多人病"},{"pid":"406a205192eb07038aa8d5f044d6933ed8339a78","tid":1405954,"uid":267235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:13:06.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位推post<br />\n<br />\n【8.5三罷】如果朝早所有人遊車河!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1404800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1404800</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cc3YftZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCc3YftZ.png&h=73d6d6c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WUfS7Za.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWUfS7Za.png&h=2961d9b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89b71b67959098d2edecf06be14a04a197c67acf","tid":1405954,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:14:38.000Z","msg":"8月5罷工集會 希望見到你 <br />\n1點鐘約定你<br />\n<br />\n旺角：麥花臣球場<br />\n黃大仙區：黃大仙廣場<br />\n沙田區：百步梯<br />\n荃灣區：荃灣公園<br />\n屯門區：屯門文娛廣場(3點開始)<br />\n大埔區：風水廣場<br />\n金鐘區：添馬公園<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fv6F2nN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffv6F2nN.png&h=477443a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3dc8155a82b3e2f3d4de8d48acfdb6c02372352a","tid":1405954,"uid":42250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:34:11.000Z","msg":"空管 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地 4/8 星期日提早一日罷工, 直頭係為左同其他市民講罷工真係可以影響社會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad29f0bd82582830580578c7610f8f90328ed981","tid":1405954,"uid":42250,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:35:45.000Z","msg":"現時民航處每日約有90名航空交通管制員負責處理機場航班升降及運作，但約三分之一的航空交通管制員今日請病假<br />\n<br />\n30個已經咁大影響 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日如果香港有30萬人已經不敢想像 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9de274170a950e6fb5b48c5f166a928a7823e2","tid":1405954,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:41:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac6785b1eda6444fa940a1362c6783d6e658be2","tid":1405954,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:44:36.000Z","msg":"- 游擊戰為主，路障戰，陷阱戰，遠攻戰，3方配合游擊戰<br />\n- 與警狗保持長距離防線，防止狗突然衝擊，可以安全退後。<br />\n- 短期防守，絕不長期守。<br />\n- 如果見到警狗開始佈防，就要立即全部人轉場地，令佢地on99咁浪費時間<br />\n- 如果沒有辦法反擊畜龍或水車，不要等待畜龍或水車出現先退後。一見到佢地身影，設路障或陷阱後就立即退後。<br />\n- 絕不硬頸，不能硬碰，更不要企硬對峙。<br />\n- 不留戀任何戰線地點，要流水式打擊，打擊完就去下一個目標。<br />\n- 聽同伴意見，不被捕為主。"},{"pid":"38f580d8ef91bbc82dfae124fb1ade9efc601dbe","tid":1405954,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd407cbeb2dde37742b48c49627bc00e79623e5","tid":1405954,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:20:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">立即成立民間記者會</span>"}]}